thread.title: Washington dam explosion injures five

author: eTN Global Editor
title: Washington dam explosion injures five
text:
Washington dam explosion injures five   
Oct 09, 2015 Priest Rapids Dam on the Columbia River   
MATTAWA, WA — Five people have been injured in an explosion of electrical equipment at Priest Rapids Dam on the Columbia River, Grant County Sheriff’s Office officials say. 
The Tri-City Herald reports that 5 Grant Public Utility District employees were injured Thursday afternoon at the dam near Mattawa. 
Multiple agencies have responded to the incident including the Hanford Fire Department.
